'''-{zh-hant:沙菲克女男爵內馬特·塔拉特·沙菲克; zh-hk:夏菲克，夏菲克女男爵}-'''，{{postnominals|country=GBR|size=100%|DBE}}（{{lang-en|Nemat Talaat Shafik}}，{{lang-ar|نعمت شفيق}}，{{bd|1962年|8月13日}}），其通稱為'''-{米努切·沙菲克}-'''（{{lang|en|Minouche Shafik}}），是[[埃及|埃及裔]]、持[[英國|英國]]與[[美國|美國]][[多重國籍|雙重國籍]]的[[经济学家|经济学家]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/public-leaders-network/2013/apr/11/nemat-shafik-minouche-global-public-leaders-lecture|title=Nemat Shafik: Global Public Leaders Series keynote speaker|last=Dudman|first=Jane|date=2013-04-11|work=The Guardian|language=en|accessdate=2020-10-20|archive-date=2017-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902045656/https://www.theguardian.com/public-leaders-network/2013/apr/11/nemat-shafik-minouche-global-public-leaders-lecture|dead-url=no}}</ref>，前[[英格兰银行|英格兰银行]]副行長<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Chan|first1=Szu Ping|last2=Quinn|first2=James|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/09/12/bank-of-england-deputy-governor-minouche-shafik-quits-after-just/|title=Bank of England deputy Governor Minouche Shafik quits after just two years|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2016-09-12|language=en-GB|accessdate=2020-10-20|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022819/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/09/12/bank-of-england-deputy-governor-minouche-shafik-quits-after-just/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，現任[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]校長<ref name="LSE2016">{{cite web|last1=The London School of Economics and Political Science|title=LSE appoints Deputy Governor of Bank of England as new Director|url=http://www.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2016/09/NewDirector.aspx|website=[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]|language=en|access-date=2020-10-20|archive-date=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016001433/http://www.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2016/09/NewDirector.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她以36歲之齡成為史上最年輕的[[世界銀行|世界銀行]]副行長前，分別於[[马萨诸塞大学阿默斯特分校|马萨诸塞大学阿默斯特分校]]與[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]獲取[[文学士|文学士]]和[[理學碩士|理學碩士]]兩個學位，以及到[[牛津大學聖安東尼學院|牛津大學聖安東尼學院]]攻讀[[哲學博士|哲學博士]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/the-prime-minister-has-reappointed-dame-minouche-shafik-and-muriel-gray-as-trustees-of-the-british-museum|title=The Prime Minister has reappointed Baroness Minouche Shafik and Muriel Gray as Trustees of the British Museum.|website=GOV.UK|language=en|access-date=2020-10-20|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221090248/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/the-prime-minister-has-reappointed-dame-minouche-shafik-and-muriel-gray-as-trustees-of-the-british-museum|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後，她回到英國{{le|國際發展部|Department for International Development}}擔任[[常務次官|常務次官]]，2011年卸任後成為[[國際貨幣基金組織|國際貨幣基金組織]]副總裁<ref>{{Cite web |title=LSE appoints Deputy Governor of Bank of England as new Director  |url=http://www.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2016/09/NewDirector.aspx |work=[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]] |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913165923/https://www2.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2016/09/NewDirector.aspx |archive-date=2016-09-13 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2020年，獲提名晉爵，是為-{zh-hant:沙菲克女男爵; zh-hk:夏菲克女男爵}-，於[[英國上議院|上議院]]以[[中立議員|中立議員]]身份議政。

